      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It has been such a reliable companion and is still in wonderful shape! It drives super smooth, the interior is nice and clean, and it\u2019s clearly been well-loved over the years. If you're looking for a dependable set of wheels that\u2019s ready for your next road trip, this is the one for you. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner will absolutely love it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 32000.0,
