    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver\u2019s specification featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for optimal volumetric efficiency across the powerband. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission offers precise shift gates, delivering torque to the rear wheels via a Variable M Differential Lock. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced to mitigate chassis fatigue, and the rod bearings have been serviced to ensure long-term reciprocating assembly health. The suspension retains its factory-tuned damping characteristics with refreshed bushings for sharp turn-in and lateral stability. While the exterior shows honest signs of road use, the mechanical telemetry and drivetrain integrity are excellent.",
      "price": 34500.0,
